title: Wealthsimple Trade Account Setup: Free trading app Canada, UK, USA
description:
I walk through the step by step process of setting up a Wealthsimple trade account, connect in to a bank account, deposit funds and add stocks to my watchlist all on the free trading app: Wealthsimple Trade. Free apps like this are invaluable resources to young investors and can allow individuals to setup RRSP and TFSA accounts and trade stocks in the account. I will continue to follow up with trade ideas in this account so we can see how the money will grow over time using automatic deposits and reinvesting dividends month after month.

Follow all of my trades: https://www.patreon.com/drawbridgefinance
14 Rules that Made Levi Rich Video: https://youtu.be/7oPmnfoIuwE
